    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏的灵感来自与朋友们畅玩的乐趣。Blam! Blam! 是一款俯视射击游戏，可与多达11个朋友一起参与。当最少7人参与语音聊天，彼此问我们今晚玩什么时，乐趣马上就来了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以选择公平组队或者由你来带领大家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最有乐趣的游戏模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择一张地图，战斗至最后一人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras/e5162522ad2c10836249bfa178de4ef1.avif?t=1770844562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras_big/e5162522ad2c10836249bfa178de4ef1.avif?t=1770844562 width=800 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走廊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras/37393a06030e39a877c7f87a698602c8.avif?t=1770844562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras_big/37393a06030e39a877c7f87a698602c8.avif?t=1770844562 width=800 height=536 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城堡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras/868aae5393f19c6435596707913c0104.avif?t=1770844562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras_big/868aae5393f19c6435596707913c0104.avif?t=1770844562 width=800 height=558 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仓库</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras/cffa5e461142586f5c1111e238343a8f.avif?t=1770844562\" width=800 height=628 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用最趁手的武器。在比赛中重复使用同一件武器可增强其威力。去夺取那把金色哇塞枪吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149730/extras/eb2a7c0f4a8dd888f6aad7201006b207.avif?t=1770844562\" width=722 height=114 /></span></p>",
